text:
This is my favorite go to place for comfort food.  Love their carna asada fries.  Then I always add some carrots & onions. 
Sadly their customer service is up & down.  You don't get the same quality every time.

I've been here many times during my 10 years of living on the East side.  This place is always so dirty. Also, it's really annoying that the people taking orders don't speak english! They forgot items in my order this past weekend. I'm done with this crappy location.

Been here many times! Their C/Asada Fries are to die for! It costs $8.76 at the moment. 

They are open 24 Hours! Inside cleanliness is decent but is comparable to Taco's El Gordo. 

Overall good taco shop on the east side!
Absolutely horrible I mean seriously what fucking idiot shoves 8+ chicken tacos in one box!!! Fuck you and tour broken ass chicken tacos putos
I'm very unsatisfied. There was a fly inside my drink. My food is never great and they don't ever give me the amount of salsas I ask for.
